{"id":131194,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/01/图辑：巴西首位女总统宣誓就职/","date":"2011-01-03T07:39:06Z","modified":"2011-01-03T07:39:06Z","title":"图辑：巴西首位女总统宣誓就职","content":"<div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div><a href=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2011/01/02/110102035750_brazil_rousseff_01_reuters_926x521_reuters.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"接载巴西新任总统迪尔玛·罗塞夫的车队向着首都巴西利亚的国会大楼进发（1/1/2011）\" height=\"60\" src=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/ic/106x60/www.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2011/01/02/110102035750_brazil_rousseff_01_reuters_926x521_reuters.jpg\" width=\"106\" /></a></div>\n<div>2011年元旦日，迪尔玛·罗塞夫正式宣誓，接替卢拉出任巴西总统。迪尔玛的就职仪式从车队环城绕行开始，她被安排搭乘一辆劳斯莱斯轿车，接受群众祝贺。</div>\n</p></div>\n</p></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div><a href=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2011/01/02/110102035919_brazil_rousseff_02_reuters_926x521_reuters.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"巴西首都巴西利亚街头民众等候接载新总统迪尔玛·罗塞夫的车队经过（1/1/2011）\" height=\"60\" src=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/ic/106x60/www.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2011/01/02/110102035919_brazil_rousseff_02_reuters_926x521_reuters.jpg\" width=\"106\" /></a></div>\n<div>当地上万名群众走到国会大楼前等候迪尔玛的到临，也有不少人是要跟卸任的卢拉道别。任满两届总统离职的卢拉一直维持着甚高的民望。</div>\n</p></div>\n</p></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div><a href=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2011/01/02/110102040212_brazil_rousseff_03_reuters_926x521_reuters.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"巴西首都巴西利亚的总统府高原宫外大批民众冒雨等候（1/1/2011）\" height=\"60\" src=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/ic/106x60/www.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2011/01/02/110102040212_brazil_rousseff_03_reuters_926x521_reuters.jpg\" width=\"106\" /></a></div>\n<div>就职仪式进行期间，巴西利亚下起了倾盘大雨，但对民众的热情丝毫</p>\n","author":176,"categories":[8779],"tags":[]}